text:
 Sunday


x Sunday 2nd August at [[Eagle Creek, Humphreys County, Tennessee|Egle Creek]] Meeting house
At mister [[Polly Barnett Jennings|Barnes]] at 4 o clock / {[shorthand?]}

 Sunday


x Sunday 9th at the [[Sulphur Wells Academy, Henry County, Tennessee|Academy]] by Col [[Solomon Copeland|Copelands]]
2 Cor 9 = 3 = 4 = {[shorthand?]}

 Saturday


2nd {shorthand} preached at Mr [[Cyrus Starrett|Starretts]] {shorthand}
Spent the night at [[Benjamin Kent|Benj Kent's]] Distance 6 miles

 Tuesday


19th Mr [[Gideon J. Newton|G. B. Newton]] returned to the Island 
&amp; brought several other [[Baptist|Baptist]] Priest with 
him to hold a protracted meeting {shorthand}
{shorthand}

 Friday


6th passed through Joackson [[Wooster, Wayne County, Ohio|Woster]] &amp; [[Loudonville, Richland County, Ohio|Loudenville]] &amp; 
spent the ninght at the Inn of [[William Elliot|Wm Elliot]] 41

 Sunday


8th Sunday I preached at the School house {shorthand}
rode to [[James Ivins|James Ivins]] &amp; spent the night 4 m

 Thursday


17 Rode to Br [[John Jackson|Jackson's]] &amp; met With Elder [[Elias F. Wells|Wells]]. Preached at Br Jacksons {Was followed by Elders Wells and [[Abraham Owen Smoot|Smoot]]} 
after meeting travled to Br [[John H. Williams|H. Williams]] distance of the day 16 miles

 Sunday


Aprail 17th Sunday preached at the School house on [[Damon Creek, Calloway County, Kentucky|Damonds Creek]] &amp; baptized one Jn Thomas
and Preached at night at Sister [[Celia Parker|Parkers]] to a large congregation {shorthand}

 Wednesday


29 June Preached at Mr [[Alexander McKinzie|McKinzie's]] held a debate with a [[Baptist|Baptist]] Priest after meeting &amp; 
selling a [[Book of Mormon|Book of Mormon]] to McKinzie we Rode to Mr [[David Crider|David Criders]] [[Gibson County, Tennessee|Gibson Co]] Tenn 7 m

 Saturday


6 Preached at Mr [[Randolph Alexander|Alexanders]] and Baptized 2 [[Jeremiah B. Murphy|Brother]] &amp; [[Levinah W. Jackson Murphy|Sister Murphy]] {[[Jeremiah B. Murphy|Brother Murphy]] was dissatisfied because he had not received the [[Holy Ghost|Holy Ghost]] as he expected. Probably looking for a person was not [illegible] the
[cause/case]. We told him to consider the subject well.}

 Wednesday


14 Spent the day at Brother [[Johnson F. Lane|Lane's]] in writings felt some unwell {in consequence of an uncommon bile or biles} 
in the evening walked to Br [[John Camp|Camp's]] was quite lame at night 5 miles

Blank Rook Journal No. 1.
Journal of (Lewis Allen) {shorthand}
W Woodruff

I preached upon the scattering &amp; gathering
of Israel {shorthand}
{shorthand}

 Tuesday

19 I spent the day at [[Aphek Woodruff, b. 1778|fathers]] house &amp;
Preached at candle light upon the authenticity
of the Book of Mormon {shorthand}

 Sunday


21 Sunday I spoke at [[Brigham City, Apache County, Arizona Territory|Brigham City]] followed 
By [[Lot Smith|Lot Smith]] I spoke the 2d tim {shorthand}

 Wednesday


24. [FIGURE] I wrote 2 letters to [[Samuel Roskelley|S. Roskelly]] &amp; 
[[Sarah Brown Woodruff|Sarah W]] Then Rode to [[St. Joseph, Apache County, Arizona Territory|St Joseph]] 25 M[iles]

